rsInfoModule.name: rsInfoModule
rsInfoModule.contactinfo: Ella Yu WatchGuard Technologies, Inc. 1841 Zanker Road San Jose, CA 95112 USA 408-519-4888 ella.yu@watchguard.com
rsInfoModule.description: The MIB module describes various system statistics information of RapidStream system.

rsSystemStatisticsMIB.name: rsSystemStatisticsMIB
rsSystemStatisticsMIB.description: This is the base system information for all system related statistical counters.

rsSystemCpuUtil.name: rsSystemCpuUtil
rsSystemCpuUtil.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 5 seconds. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.

rsSystemTotalSendBytes.name: rsSystemTotalSendBytes
rsSystemTotalSendBytes.description: The total number of bytes sent since system is up. This number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

rsSystemTotalRecvBytes.name: rsSystemTotalRecvBytes
rsSystemTotalRecvBytes.description: The total number of bytes received since system is up. This number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

rsSystemTotalSendPackets.name: rsSystemTotalSendPackets
rsSystemTotalSendPackets.description: The total number of the packets sent since system is up. This number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

rsSystemTotalRecvPackets.name: rsSystemTotalRecvPackets
rsSystemTotalRecvPackets.description: The total number of the packets received since system is up. The number includes both cut through traffic and host traffic.

rsSystemStreamReqTotal.name: rsSystemStreamReqTotal
rsSystemStreamReqTotal.description: The total number of the connection requests since system is up.

rsSystemStreamReqDrop.name: rsSystemStreamReqDrop
rsSystemStreamReqDrop.description: The total number of the connection requests being dropped since system is up.

rsSystemCpuUtil1.name: rsSystemCpuUtil1
rsSystemCpuUtil1.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 1 minute. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.

rsSystemCpuUtil5.name: rsSystemCpuUtil5
rsSystemCpuUtil5.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 5 minutes. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.

rsSystemCpuUtil15.name: rsSystemCpuUtil15
rsSystemCpuUtil15.description: CPU utilization of the system in last 15 minutes. The value is measured in 0.01%. For example, if the value is 234, then CPU utilization is 2.34%.
